title: Ethereum Foundation Sells 1,700 $ETH Worth Over $2.7 Million, Still Holds $500 Million
description: The Ethereum Foundation has, through the decentralized cryptocurrency exchange Uniswap, sold 1,700 Ether ($ETH) for $2.73 million worth of USDC, in their largest single transaction of the year. According to on-chain monitoring service Spot On Chain, the Ethereum Foundation’s transaction helped the total amount of ETH the organization sold so far this year reach 2,262 […]
